    "originContent": "## Environment variable overrides",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "Todos los parámetros OAuth pueden ser sobreescritos mediante variables de entorno. Si Anthropic cambia algo antes de que publiquemos una actualización, configura una variable de entorno y sigue trabajando:"
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "wJh9R+MetHXcny0N+HlRJPZ7knkW3lRDG5tGfbJ63DY=",
    "originContent": "All OAuth parameters can be overridden via environment variables. If Anthropic changes something before we publish an update, set an env var and keep working:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "| Variable | Descripción |  "
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "Ekm+WxRGQZfraruJY6ZuncjJW1O298YosVHARNj0EoM=",
    "originContent": "| Variable | Description |",
    "translatedContent": "|---|---|"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "QZm6RU1tOug2VxIMK7a9Z07vwN19PNTMhEFx3GclE1s=",
    "originContent": "|---|---|",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "PRApVc8NLIC6cTPH88vDjTxlEIsBwkEU7/+WmRd5p88=",
    "originContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_CLIENT_ID` | OAuth client ID |",
    "translatedContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_CLIENT_ID` | ID de cliente OAuth |"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "8LaELggeDEfFRs/jqQTuK7zJVMqlcP1FRij9octjAbI=",
    "originContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_CLI_VERSION` | Claude CLI version for User-Agent |",
    "translatedContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_CLI_VERSION` | Versión de Claude CLI para User-Agent |"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "NuniNTBPuVuAV26fY7v9ULc7NTaa4s/Pk+6tsC94UZc=",
    "originContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_USER_AGENT` | Full User-Agent string (overrides version) |",
    "translatedContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_USER_AGENT` | Cadena completa de User-Agent (sobrescribe la versión) |"
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "CLMg5y30bO9WJtt/ocS74xEuth2mPA70S6HYL0bTu3I=",
    "originContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_AUTHORIZE_URL` | OAuth authorization endpoint |",
    "translatedContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_AUTHORIZE_URL` | Punto final de autorización OAuth |"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "oxNDrmcmKr1sLyCIYrZfbtAq75b7S4t5wxtldm7cVv8=",
    "originContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_TOKEN_URL` | OAuth token endpoint |",
    "translatedContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_TOKEN_URL` | Punto final de token OAuth |"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "I0eTIcUUB9nrrthoKdNYXZULMH4jE7Hv5Q93dWLBVS0=",
    "originContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_REDIRECT_URI` | OAuth redirect URI |",
    "translatedContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_REDIRECT_URI` | URI de redirección OAuth |"
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "g1gK3wBYBtsugqP7sW3oIoV80NtV7cz1zRXPGx3IDHE=",
    "originContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_SCOPES` | OAuth scopes |",
    "translatedContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_SCOPES` | Alcances OAuth |"
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "wjQ3ctEmoo5RCwZbBcBDAQDcKQ/tTpfbS4jxSdWCcl4=",
    "originContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_BETA_FLAGS` | Anthropic beta feature flags |",
    "translatedContent": "| `ANTHROPIC_BETA_FLAGS` | Banderas de funciones beta de Anthropic |"
  },
